Pre-Game Insights: England manager Gareth Southgate should not risk captain Harry Kane for the friendly.
Luke Shaw, Harry Maguire, Anthony Gordon, Jude Bellingham, Kobbie Mainoo, Phil Foden and Kyle Walker will join the team later after their club commitments.
Cole Palmer, most likely with Eberechi Eze, will start instead of Bukayo Saka.
Declan Rice and Conor Gallagher are ahead of Adam Wharton in the pecking order.
Marc Guehi and Lewis Dunk are expected to benefit in the backline.
